Function_demonstration_2.message: I will guide you through the first section 'Paste Upload' to demonstrate the usage of Panluo upload. You can also choose other demonstrations.

Function_demonstration_6.message: 'Paste Upload' is a convenient file upload feature that supports directly pasting image data, image links, or local files into the upload box for quick upload. It eliminates the need for cumbersome selection steps, allowing you to simply copy and paste to upload files.

Function_demonstration_8.message: 'Drag and Drop Upload' is a convenient file upload method. You can simply drag files from your local computer and drop them into the designated area to complete the upload. It allows for quick dragging and dropping of multiple files and frequent file uploads, improving work efficiency and providing users with a convenient and comfortable upload experience.

Function_demonstration_10.message: 'Right-click Upload' is a convenient file upload method available in the browser's right-click menu. Users can simply right-click on an image on the webpage and choose the upload option to complete the file upload. It allows users to quickly upload images while browsing the web.
